1.Setup

For develop:

python setup.py develop


2.Run: 

cd lightrest && pecan serve config.py

or

cd lightrest && python start.py


3.Other issue

Check the pecan/rest.py line 386

Maybe, you need to modify the code

controller = self._find_controller(
   '%s_%s' % (method, method_name.replace('-', '_')),
   method_name.replace('-', '_')
)
